<br />\n利申聽講<br />\n<br />\nbtw 中國佬 無限好"},{"pid":"8c6616425fdb6b311a3a2ceb42fa85007b3df023","tid":119231,"uid":16112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:53:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金門精神 做撚死人<br />\n<br />\n利申聽講<br />\n<br />\nbtw 中國佬 無限好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金門精神 做撚死人<br />\n我都聽過<br />\n講多少少，我個friend 係澳門做開，佢話project 完左俾人炒左，因為香港冇job, 但係公司就keep左成班鬼，冇production之餘仲搞9做個d，另外project一少d就炒人，多返project又唔請人，個個要一條友就幾條友野。<br />\n佢話有單仆街野我想知係咪真。話說澳門有條友俾公司炒左，公司補足俾佢。但2星期後公司想用返佢，佢都想返但HR要佢俾返晒d錢公司當2星期放no pay , 有冇人聽過？"},{"pid":"53936307bec2b4c3cc8caa254f005b13f5233363","tid":119231,"uid":16112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:58:32.000Z","msg":"想知多少少，唔想上賊船<br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"1090c4f2258e23adda423145a59765d3da70068d","tid":119231,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T08:05:12.000Z","msg":"金門先hea wo<br />\n睇高鐵就知"},{"pid":"de7b98284fc7cdfac6c0d85b29a7d70ce7ebe5a4","tid":119231,"uid":16112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T08:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金門先hea wo<br />\n睇高鐵就知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一直都係聽做撚死人，第一次聽金門hea<br />\n<br />\n師兄係金門人？"},{"pid":"bdfb29118a3ee87d6ccb8d1770e0881d7dcf0ba7","tid":119231,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T08:36:37.000Z","msg":"XX精神 做撚死人<br />\n間間公司名都放得落去嫁啦...ON9"},{"pid":"8b869ab3a637b7ad39ddc656717cc9a5eed72ffc","tid":119231,"uid":46722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T09:05:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金門精神 做撚死人<br />\n<br />\n利申聽講<br />\n<br />\nbtw 中國佬 無限好</blockquote><br />\n中國佬<br />\n死得早"},{"pid":"1465bf2acda81cce01086d57d8f5af91fc4024e7","tid":119231,"uid":16112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T09:05:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>XX精神 做撚死人<br />\n間間公司名都放得落去嫁啦...ON9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以咪要問咁多位師兄攞資料"},{"pid":"233b2347d6290987f4c7caf8f6d5970352c44a3e","tid":119231,"uid":63700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T09:12:42.000Z","msg":"好辛苦，啲人好中意缷膊<br />\n利申老豆係管理層"},{"pid":"6b1c48c498f43bd7573fcbacd1e01f453f5ad33f","tid":119231,"uid":70192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T09:22:51.000Z","msg":"金門做到仆街"},{"pid":"7986e281a2726446da77d1764aa5e693a9e6e8bc","tid":119231,"uid":16112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:20:47.000Z","msg":"看來都係睇定d，費時為左多少少錢搞到自己做得唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n辛苦唔緊要，最怕夾屎忽鬼"},{"pid":"ca9558e6fcf5d00156c2e79815550d77a11c5166","tid":119231,"uid":77746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:32:12.000Z","msg":"做左金門intern幾星期.....<br />\n做QS team嗰邊<br />\n表示做到隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2adb233408b12353aa9d33d2361303d293dccf8e","tid":119231,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"Zero harm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8a05280d9c1025271d5b1c538a23545f825a58","tid":119231,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:16:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>金門精神 做撚死人<br />\n<br />\n利申聽講<br />\n<br />\nbtw 中國佬 無限好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金門精神 做撚死人<br />\n我都聽過<br />\n講多少少，我個friend 係澳門做開，佢話project 完左俾人炒左，因為香港冇job, 但係公司就keep左成班鬼，冇production之餘仲搞9做個d，另外project一少d就炒人，多返project又唔請人，個個要一條友就幾條友野。<br />\n佢話有單仆街野我想知係咪真。<span style=\"color: red;\">話說澳門有條友俾公司炒左，公司補足俾佢。但2星期後公司想用返佢，佢都想返但HR要佢俾返晒d錢公司當2星期放no pay</span> , 有冇人聽過？</blockquote><br />\n痴撚線"},{"pid":"c7ace0f9ff98aaf244b03fe599dda2bc95ef49ac","tid":119231,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:24:20.000Z","msg":"請左你先問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ea91464f5dd0bc18140c862235ca81e5c3ef11","tid":119231,"uid":28758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:51:59.000Z","msg":"好過新昌俊和中國佬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ddc69d5ea9a92dee572f9315a10eac3a69c10f0","tid":119231,"uid":16112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>金門精神 做撚死人<br />\n<br />\n利申聽講<br />\n<br />\nbtw 中國佬 無限好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金門精神 做撚死人<br />\n我都聽過<br />\n講多少少，我個friend 係澳門做開，佢話project 完左俾人炒左，因為香港冇job, 但係公司就keep左成班鬼，冇production之餘仲搞9做個d，另外project一少d就炒人，多返project又唔請人，個個要一條友就幾條友野。<br />\n佢話有單仆街野我想知係咪真。<span style=\"color: red;\">話說澳門有條友俾公司炒左，公司補足俾佢。但2星期後公司想用返佢，佢都想返但HR要佢俾返晒d錢公司當2星期放no pay</span> , 有冇人聽過？</blockquote><br />\n痴撚線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得痴撚線，咁大間公司，唔係咁仆街掛！我先前在想係咪我個friend俾人炒左所以作故仔，但又覺得佢冇理由點我，所以先問下咁多位大佬"},{"pid":"ee739eec83805a01b3032082a72aed4598bd13c2","tid":119231,"uid":16112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:59:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請左你先問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請左先問就等於上左賊船先問有冇賊la"},{"pid":"3d96665ac29a61cb54a52926c0a6d3c86d43875c","tid":119231,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:00:05.000Z","msg":"呀爸做金門"},{"pid":"056a7ba81f54ad75c3eaa831f0acdce8b6e676e9","tid":119231,"uid":28758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>請左你先問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請左先問就等於上左賊船先問有冇賊la</blockquote><br />\n其實都係睇team睇盤既姐"},{"pid":"30a2a9b3f9c4e1c03eabe92a59635bc456cc60aa","tid":119231,"uid":41299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:19:34.000Z","msg":"內部Audit好密好嚴格<br />\n要有心理準備固定OT<br />\n通常起貨期好短 夾野要好急<br />\n好多安全堂要上<br />\n<br />\n不過好多HR覺得金門係好野<br />\n而且training老實講唔差<br />\n對日後幾有幫助<br />\n<br />\n簡單一句 當金門跳板啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}